1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,070
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,070 --> 00:00:03,680
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:05,310
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:08,050
(Episode 86)

5
00:00:15,520 --> 00:00:16,690
(Under Maintenance)

6
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:37,240
My...

7
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,440
My allergy medication is gone.

8
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:42,950
Don't tell me Park Tae Ho...

9
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,360
(Under Maintenance)

10
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:01,030
(Park Min Jun)

11
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:27,590
Perhaps it's the chestnuts
that were added,

12
00:01:29,790 --> 00:01:31,900
but this barley tea
tastes excellent.

13
00:01:47,050 --> 00:01:48,050
Now,

14
00:01:49,210 --> 00:01:51,850
another ten minutes locked in there
should do it.

15
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,790
- I took care of all CCTV footage.
- So,

16
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:58,120
what'll happen
with the reinvestigation?

17
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:02,290
The committee reviewing the case
meets tomorrow.

18
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:03,560
Well,

19
00:02:04,130 --> 00:02:07,870
other than Baek Jin Ju's testimony,
there's no solid evidence.

20
00:02:08,970 --> 00:02:11,670
So what'll happen
if Baek Jin Ju dies?

21
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:17,510
They won't bother reopening it
if there's no one demanding justice.

22
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:21,680
So we just need
to wrap this up nicely.

23
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:26,150
We just need to establish our alibis
to prove we were never here.

24
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:30,990
We should probably get going,
just in case any problems arise.

25
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:36,030
Right. I should see
what Kim Dan Hui is up to anyway.

26
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:42,870
I made her feel guilty
about Baek Jun Gi's death,

27
00:02:43,130 --> 00:02:45,800
and now that Baek Jin Ju is dead,

28
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:49,040
she'll spend the rest of her life
blaming herself,

29
00:02:49,610 --> 00:02:52,040
completely crushed by the guilt.

30
00:03:03,690 --> 00:03:05,190
Really? Of all the days...

31
00:03:06,620 --> 00:03:08,030
Why isn't she answering her phone?

32
00:03:10,130 --> 00:03:11,430
Darn.

33
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:19,000
- Yes, it's me.
- What about Jin Ju? Is she okay?

34
00:03:19,070 --> 00:03:21,410
I got your call,
and I'm on my way up.

35
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:24,540
I can't reach her, but I'll call you
as soon as I find her.

36
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:27,080
Okay, I'm almost there too.

37
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:30,620
- Please hurry and find Jin Ju.
- Okay. Call me when you get here.

38
00:03:31,850 --> 00:03:33,280
(Emergency Stairwell)

39
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:13,520
Min Jun, Jin Ju's not
at the teahouse.

40
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:16,690
Wait, that's Jin Ju's purse. How...

41
00:04:17,930 --> 00:04:19,500
Something must've happened.

42
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,430
We have to find her.
She can't have gone far.

43
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:22,930
- Hurry.
- What?

44
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:23,940
Shoot!

45
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:28,670
What do you mean Jin Ju's missing?

46
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,810
James called.

47
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:33,040
She went to see Detective Yun
about the reinvestigation,

48
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:35,510
- and now she's missing.
- What?

49
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:40,520
Park Tae Ho. It was Park Tae Ho.

50
00:04:41,090 --> 00:04:45,060
He used Detective Yun to set a trap.
That murderer.

51
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:48,090
How could he do this
to Jin Ju again?

52
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:51,700
Dan Hui.

53
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,300
Dan Hui!

54
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:56,400
Park Tae Ho!

55
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,770
You have some nerve.

56
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:05,340
What... Hey.

57
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:08,410
What did you do to Jin Ju?

58
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:10,420
How could you hurt her again?

59
00:05:17,090 --> 00:05:18,360
Has something happened...

60
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,160
to Baek Jin Ju?

61
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:24,060
Don't you dare play dumb.

62
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:28,100
You used Detective Yun
to lure and kidnap Jin Ju.

63
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:29,470
I did?

64
00:05:30,170 --> 00:05:31,840
That's absurd.

65
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:37,280
Besides, I doubt there's any proof
Detective Yun was even there.

66
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:41,750
You shouldn't make accusations
without evidence.

67
00:05:42,850 --> 00:05:44,880
I knew you were inhuman,

68
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:48,090
but I thought
even your evil had a limit.

69
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:52,890
You're being consumed
by your own sins.

70
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:56,360
To cover up killing my sister,
you had to kill Dr. Baek.

71
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:59,900
And to keep his murder buried,
you harmed Jin Ju too.

72
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,300
You...

73
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,840
are going to be bitten...

74
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:07,000
and torn apart by your own sins...

75
00:06:07,770 --> 00:06:09,510
until you meet a miserable end.

76
00:06:09,910 --> 00:06:10,940
That's on you...

77
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:14,250
for digging up things
you should've left alone!

78
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:17,010
If Baek Jin Ju is dead,

79
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:19,080
that's entirely...

80
00:06:19,980 --> 00:06:21,020
on you,

81
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:22,850
Kim Dan Hui.

82
00:06:27,490 --> 00:06:28,490
Park Tae Ho!

83
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:30,460
Sir...

84
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,930
Sir, are you all right?

85
00:06:33,130 --> 00:06:35,070
What's going on?

86
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:40,200
If anything happens to Jin Ju,

87
00:06:40,810 --> 00:06:42,440
I'll kill you with my own two hands.

88
00:06:42,570 --> 00:06:45,110
Even if it means
getting blood on them,

89
00:06:45,410 --> 00:06:48,210
I'll make sure you die. So talk.

90
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:51,050
Where's Jin Ju?
What did you do to her?

91
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:57,220
Making a scene here
won't bring Baek Jin Ju back.

92
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:01,060
What are you all waiting for?
Drag her out of here!

93
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,160
Right.

94
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:06,130
Get out.
Get out of my house this instant.

95
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:09,170
Park Tae Ho...
No, let me go. Park Tae Ho!

96
00:07:09,770 --> 00:07:12,270
Where's Jin Ju? Park Tae Ho!

97
00:07:19,810 --> 00:07:21,510
She's looking for Baek Jin Ju?

98
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:25,150
Instead of accusing me
of killing her,

99
00:07:25,650 --> 00:07:27,550
she's demanding I hand her over?

100
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:32,690
Check again and find out
what happened to Baek Jin Ju.

101
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,530
Yes, sir.

102
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:40,670
Baek Jin Ju...

103
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:46,570
Let go of me.

104
00:07:48,010 --> 00:07:49,010
Let me go.

105
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:54,310
Did Park Tae Ho kill
Baek Jin Ju again?

106
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,050
Who said anything about dying?

107
00:07:57,320 --> 00:08:00,450
Our Jin Ju's definitely coming back
safe and sound.

108
00:08:01,090 --> 00:08:02,250
"Our" Jin Ju?

109
00:08:03,450 --> 00:08:05,660
Were you two that close?

110
00:08:07,330 --> 00:08:08,560
Do you know anything?

111
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:11,560
If you know
what Park Tae Ho did to Jin Ju,

112
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,500
you'd better tell me.

113
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,200
What would I know?

114
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:18,240
I only just found out
that Chloe is Baek Jin Ju.

115
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:19,340
Besides,

116
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:22,770
our deal only covers
the slush fund ledger.

117
00:08:23,210 --> 00:08:25,680
It's not like we have
a tight partnership.

118
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:28,750
Still. We have to save Jin Ju,
no matter what.

119
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:31,920
Find out anything you can
and tell me.

120
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,150
If anything happens to Jin Ju,

121
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:38,560
I'll destroy everything,
whether it's Adele or Park Tae Ho.

122
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,230
She genuinely cares for Baek Jin Ju.

123
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:49,630
Wait a minute.

124
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:54,170
The person who cares most
about her is Hyun Jun.

125
00:08:56,010 --> 00:08:58,580
Will he be shaken by the news?

126
00:08:59,010 --> 00:09:00,340
It'll be a disaster...

127
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:02,650
if he tries to save her
and Park Tae Ho catches him.

128
00:09:07,050 --> 00:09:10,150
Geun Tae, where are you?

129
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:12,660
Actually, where's Hyun Jun?

130
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,830
Find him, now!

131
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,830
Look, you can't just make wild accusations
without any proof.

132
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:24,870
Hold on.

133
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,510
I'm telling you,
Jin Ju is in real danger!

134
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:29,810
You need to arrest
Chairman Park of Adele Group...

135
00:09:29,810 --> 00:09:31,380
and start investigating right away.

136
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:34,050
Actually, you need to investigate
Deputy Chief Yun first.

137
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:36,950
She went missing after meeting him.

138
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,320
Detective Yun. Stop right there!

139
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:46,390
What did you do to Jin Ju?
Tell me the truth.

140
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:49,330
- What are you talking about?
- What?

141
00:09:49,330 --> 00:09:50,700
Where's Jin Ju?

142
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:53,260
Have you both lost it?

143
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,930
Why are you coming to me
looking for Baek Jin Ju?

144
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
What?

145
00:09:57,570 --> 00:09:59,970
She had an appointment
to meet with you.

146
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:04,080
Something came up,
so I had to ask for a raincheck.

147
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:07,080
I have an alibi. Feel free to check.

148
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,180
Why you...

149
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:09,250
Unbelievable.

150
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:10,580
Hey!

151
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,350
You both saw that, right?

152
00:10:14,650 --> 00:10:17,560
Threatening a police officer
right in front of the station?

153
00:10:17,890 --> 00:10:18,960
How about it?

154
00:10:19,290 --> 00:10:21,790
- Want me to throw you in a cell?
- What?

155
00:10:22,130 --> 00:10:23,260
Calm down, sir. Please.

156
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:26,960
If you guys want to find someone,
file a missing person report first.

157
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,370
That's right.

158
00:10:28,370 --> 00:10:32,070
Stop harassing innocent people
and file a proper report.

159
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,340
The only reason
I'm tolerating this...

160
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:36,040
is because I'm facing
a disciplinary hearing.

161
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,980
Coming through!

162
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:43,480
- Hey, wait!
- Sir, please don't.

163
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:44,950
Stop it. That's enough.

164
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:48,250
He took her.
You have to investigate him now.

165
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:52,190
- Where's Jin Ju?
- Where is she? Where's Jin Ju?

166
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:54,090
Bring her back, you jerk!

167
00:10:57,530 --> 00:10:59,930
Judging by their reactions,
they're not lying.

168
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:03,770
Baek Jin Ju isn't dead.
She's missing.

169
00:11:04,470 --> 00:11:06,600
She didn't die trapped
in the elevator.

170
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,240
It seems she just disappeared.

171
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:12,880
How incompetent can you be?

172
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:15,080
Find Baek Jin Ju.

173
00:11:15,450 --> 00:11:16,680
And when you do,

174
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:18,320
kill her!

175
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:49,880
What happened?

176
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,360
Park Hyun Jun?

177
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:11,440
What happened? Did you save me?

178
00:12:14,370 --> 00:12:15,510
How's everything coming along?

179
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:17,210
Couldn't be better, sir.

180
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:20,950
We have to wrap this up
before they decide to reinvestigate,

181
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,710
so today is our only shot.

182
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:26,480
Yes, sir. It's all set up according
to your exact instructions.

183
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:38,130
Wrapping it up
before they decide to reinvestigate?

184
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:42,300
Are they going after Jin Ju?

185
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,400
Whatever.

186
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:49,210
Min Jun will take care of it.

187
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,600
(Personal Profile: Baek Jin Ju)

188
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:26,310
(Severe chestnut allergy)

189
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:27,380
(On Seodam)

190
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:10,150
Is everything cleared up now?

191
00:14:10,990 --> 00:14:12,890
- Is that why...
- Don't get the wrong idea.

192
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:15,390
I only helped you
because I wanted us...

193
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:17,860
to have a proper goodbye.

194
00:14:19,230 --> 00:14:21,100
A proper goodbye?

195
00:14:21,830 --> 00:14:22,870
Our marriage...

196
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,270
needs to be officially over.

197
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,180
Hyun Jun.

198
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,020
This won't end with you leaving me.

199
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,890
It will end with me leaving you.

200
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:53,830
It's simple since we never
registered our marriage.

201
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:58,270
Hyun Jun.

202
00:14:59,370 --> 00:15:01,340
Don't do this. Let's...

203
00:15:03,770 --> 00:15:06,580
Why? You don't need this anymore.

204
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:08,980
This marriage...

205
00:15:10,050 --> 00:15:11,080
or me.

206
00:15:21,690 --> 00:15:23,560
I don't need you anymore either.

207
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:27,200
I said I'd give you everything,

208
00:15:29,430 --> 00:15:31,300
but all I got in return
was betrayal.

209
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:34,540
Depending on others?

210
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:37,040
I'm done with that now.

211
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:42,510
And being played for a fool...

212
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:46,650
I've had more than enough.

213
00:15:57,760 --> 00:15:58,760
Wait.

214
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,000
I never abandoned you,

215
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,810
and I never thought
you were useless.

216
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:13,140
I felt guilty using you
for my revenge,

217
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:15,810
but I was always grateful for
how you stayed by my side...

218
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:18,180
through it all.

219
00:16:21,990 --> 00:16:24,720
You were so sincere with me,

220
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,690
and I'm sorry...

221
00:16:29,860 --> 00:16:32,000
that all I gave you in return
was betrayal.

222
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:34,300
Even now,

223
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,870
I want you to walk away
from this fight...

224
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:39,440
and live in peace.

225
00:16:42,210 --> 00:16:43,210
Now?

226
00:16:45,410 --> 00:16:46,680
You're telling me to walk away?

227
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:50,210
I get it. You're just trying
to ease your own guilt...

228
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:51,580
by getting me to walk away.

229
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,920
I'm going to see this fight
to the end.

230
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:01,990
Not for the sake of your revenge,

231
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:05,200
but for myself,
so I can live as Park Hyun Jun.

232
00:17:05,430 --> 00:17:07,060
As Chairman Park Tae Ho's son,

233
00:17:07,130 --> 00:17:09,100
I'll become the owner
of the Adele Group.

234
00:17:11,170 --> 00:17:12,540
You see, I've decided...

235
00:17:13,370 --> 00:17:16,310
to hold on to that goal
and live for it, not for you.

236
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:21,310
- Hyun Jun.
- So get your act together, too.

237
00:17:22,410 --> 00:17:23,710
Because I'm ready...

238
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:26,980
to tear down anyone
who gets in my way.

239
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:32,390
Baek Jin Ju.
I'm done going easy on you.

240
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:36,090
Next time, even if you're dying,

241
00:17:38,860 --> 00:17:40,660
I won't save you.

242
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:45,000
So you'd better watch your own back.

243
00:18:20,470 --> 00:18:26,680
(Head of Division 2, Park Hyun Jun)

244
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:35,390
- Park Hyun Jun.
- Hyun Jun.

245
00:18:37,890 --> 00:18:40,820
Hyun Jun, have you been
at the office this whole time?

246
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:44,500
Do you know or not?

247
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:46,900
What? About Baek Jin Ju?

248
00:18:47,230 --> 00:18:48,470
You knew?

249
00:18:49,300 --> 00:18:51,600
It looks like
something happened to her.

250
00:18:51,840 --> 00:18:54,370
You didn't get into trouble
trying to save her, did you?

251
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,280
Baek Jin Ju...

252
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:01,580
I saved her.

253
00:19:02,610 --> 00:19:05,050
Good, Hyun Jun.
You did the right thing.

254
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:08,220
- Saving lives always comes first.
- Will you be quiet?

255
00:19:08,650 --> 00:19:09,920
If Baek Jin Ju had died,

256
00:19:09,990 --> 00:19:12,160
Hyun Jun's life
would've been ruined too.

257
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:14,630
How could he live with that guilt
for the rest of his life?

258
00:19:14,890 --> 00:19:16,530
If Park Tae Ho finds out...

259
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:19,060
and his promise
to make him chairman falls through,

260
00:19:19,130 --> 00:19:21,060
that ruins his life too.

261
00:19:21,730 --> 00:19:23,700
That stupid chairman position
isn't worth a life.

262
00:19:23,700 --> 00:19:25,570
That stupid chairman position...

263
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:28,810
is now my goal and my life.

264
00:19:31,210 --> 00:19:32,880
So you should stay out of it.

265
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:36,280
What?

266
00:19:38,850 --> 00:19:40,920
The CCTV footage
has likely been dealt with.

267
00:19:42,290 --> 00:19:43,920
I won't get caught, so don't worry.

268
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:47,930
How long are you going to let
Baek Jin Ju have a hold over you?

269
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:49,430
You said it was over.

270
00:19:49,690 --> 00:19:51,130
You said you were done with her.

271
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:54,630
It's over! I'm telling you,
it's completely over!

272
00:19:59,770 --> 00:20:02,010
Now, I just have to find a way
to take over Adele Group.

273
00:20:03,610 --> 00:20:05,410
That's all I need to think about.

274
00:20:20,690 --> 00:20:23,560
What in the world is this?

275
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:25,660
Oh my goodness.

276
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:30,130
I still hold Park Hyun Jun's secret.

277
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:33,200
If Chairman Park threatens me over
what happened with Baek Jin Ju,

278
00:20:33,370 --> 00:20:36,340
I'll just use Oh Jung Ran
and Park Hyun Jun to stop him.

279
00:20:36,970 --> 00:20:37,980
If I'm lucky,

280
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:41,010
I might even get a chance
to redeem myself with Chairman Park.

281
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:46,450
It's fine. It'll be fine.

282
00:20:46,950 --> 00:20:48,220
How will we be fine?

283
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:51,520
The Adele family has no intention
of helping us with this,

284
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:53,020
and we're about to lose everything.

285
00:20:53,020 --> 00:20:54,460
How could it possibly be fine?

286
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:00,530
Should we beg Jin Ju
for forgiveness?

287
00:21:00,600 --> 00:21:03,570
She's a kind person,
so she might forgive us.

288
00:21:05,270 --> 00:21:06,640
Dad, can't you tell?

289
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:08,870
She's not the Baek Jin Ju
we used to know.

290
00:21:08,870 --> 00:21:10,640
I just don't get it, Yu Na.

291
00:21:11,110 --> 00:21:13,380
How could you do something so evil?

292
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:17,950
It wasn't just me.
You betrayed CEO Baek first, Dad.

293
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:21,720
I did it all for our family,

294
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:24,960
- so we could live well.
- Oh, quiet down.

295
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:27,620
Is this the time
to be playing the blame game?

296
00:21:27,690 --> 00:21:30,430
We should be begging Park Tae Ho
and figuring out a way to survive.

297
00:21:31,730 --> 00:21:32,830
This won't do.

298
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,300
Until they sort this out,

299
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:38,540
I'm going to their house
and staying put.

300
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:40,100
Stop it.

301
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:43,710
Should we just sit here
and be ruined?

302
00:21:44,170 --> 00:21:47,310
I'll go. You'll only make things
more complicated.

303
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:52,050
My head's killing me. Oh my.

304
00:21:52,780 --> 00:21:53,950
What are we going to do?

305
00:21:58,420 --> 00:22:00,620
Where on earth did she disappear to?

306
00:22:04,590 --> 00:22:05,700
What brings you here?

307
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:09,530
I'm here to see the chairman.
Is something up?

308
00:22:09,730 --> 00:22:11,840
This is a family matter,
so please don't interfere.

309
00:22:12,140 --> 00:22:13,140
Please leave.

310
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:16,010
Find Baek Jin Ju at once!

311
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:19,040
Baek Jin Ju?

312
00:22:31,590 --> 00:22:32,690
What did Detective Yun say?

313
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:36,030
He says
he hasn't found any leads yet.

314
00:22:37,330 --> 00:22:39,300
That pathetic fool.

315
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:43,200
For now, focus on that James guy
who's with Baek Jin Ju.

316
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:46,040
Put a tail on him
and keep eyes on him.

317
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:48,270
If Baek Jin Ju is alive,

318
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:50,570
he's bound to make a move.

319
00:22:51,210 --> 00:22:52,210
Yes, sir.

320
00:23:01,890 --> 00:23:02,890
What?

321
00:23:04,050 --> 00:23:05,060
Are you kidding me?

322
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:07,520
How dare you barge in here?

323
00:23:08,360 --> 00:23:10,590
It sounded like
you were talking about Baek Jin Ju.

324
00:23:11,730 --> 00:23:12,930
Is she missing?

325
00:23:13,300 --> 00:23:15,330
That's right, and it's all on you.

326
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:19,440
We lost her when we tried
to take care of her again.

327
00:23:21,470 --> 00:23:23,070
We're in this mess...

328
00:23:23,070 --> 00:23:26,080
because you failed to take her out
seven years ago.

329
00:23:26,810 --> 00:23:29,810
If she reveals
what happened seven years ago,

330
00:23:31,250 --> 00:23:32,750
you'll have to face
the consequences too.

331
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:35,650
Before that happens,
please give me one more chance.

332
00:23:36,190 --> 00:23:37,190
A chance?

333
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:40,290
I'll look for Jin Ju.

334
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:43,430
I'll get close to Min Jun
and dig for information.

335
00:23:44,390 --> 00:23:47,130
Please give me a chance
to make up for my mistake.

336
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:54,640
Jin Ju.

337
00:23:56,370 --> 00:23:58,180
What on earth happened?

338
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,540
Are you hurt?
You're not injured, are you?

339
00:24:00,740 --> 00:24:02,810
- Are you all right?
- I'm fine.

340
00:24:03,810 --> 00:24:05,820
You were so worried, weren't you?
I'm sorry.

341
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:08,650
Don't say that. The only thing
that matters is that you're safe.

342
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:10,120
Jin Ju.

343
00:24:18,060 --> 00:24:19,060
Thank you.

344
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:22,100
Thank you so much
for coming back safely.

345
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:25,000
If something had happened to you,

346
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:28,410
if you'd been hurt
by Park Tae Ho again,

347
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,070
I don't think I could've handled it.

348
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:32,910
I'm okay.

349
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:35,010
I'm sorry to have worried you.

350
00:24:38,250 --> 00:24:40,880
This was Park Tae Ho's doing again,
wasn't it?

351
00:24:46,290 --> 00:24:48,960
Park Tae Ho. I knew it was him.

352
00:24:51,930 --> 00:24:52,930
How could he...

353
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:56,200
As soon as he learned she was alive,
he went after her again.

354
00:24:58,070 --> 00:25:00,770
This is unforgivable.

355
00:25:01,870 --> 00:25:03,540
I can't let him get away with this.

356
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:05,310
I'm heading over there...

357
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:08,780
to take down Park Tae Ho
and Deputy Chief Yun myself!

358
00:25:09,250 --> 00:25:10,880
Well, count me in too.

359
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:13,520
I'm going to tear them to shreds.

360
00:25:14,050 --> 00:25:16,290
Jin Ju, you should call the police
right away.

361
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:17,620
Everyone, calm down.

362
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,320
It's tough to argue
attempted murder...

363
00:25:20,390 --> 00:25:21,860
based solely
on an allergic reaction.

364
00:25:22,360 --> 00:25:23,790
What? Are you saying...

365
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:26,960
we just let this go
and let Park Tae Ho off the hook?

366
00:25:27,130 --> 00:25:29,870
We have to punish him another way.

367
00:25:30,970 --> 00:25:32,970
Do you have something else in mind?

368
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,040
Detective Yun said...

369
00:25:34,040 --> 00:25:36,240
the reinvestigation review committee
is meeting tomorrow.

370
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,110
Please confirm if that's true.

371
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:41,140
Why? If it is, are you planning
to attend the hearing?

372
00:25:41,410 --> 00:25:44,710
If Park Tae Ho finds out,
he'll try to harm you again.

373
00:25:45,450 --> 00:25:48,750
She's right. You should lie low
and be careful for now.

374
00:25:48,850 --> 00:25:51,420
Hiding won't solve anything.

375
00:25:52,420 --> 00:25:55,160
Instead, we just have to move
while keeping him in the dark.

376
00:25:55,930 --> 00:25:59,360
If we all work together,
we can evade his surveillance.

377
00:26:00,930 --> 00:26:03,500
I need everyone's help.

378
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:10,040
Okay, let's do it.

379
00:26:10,770 --> 00:26:13,440
This time, we'll help you, Jin Ju.

380
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:23,590
(Adele)

381
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,820
Is the press conference ready?

382
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:31,260
Yes. I'll expose my father
at the press conference...

383
00:26:31,530 --> 00:26:32,930
and build public support
for a reinvestigation.

384
00:26:34,730 --> 00:26:37,400
We have to keep Jin Ju safe
until then.

385
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:42,570
Okay. I'll check on things
at the company and keep you posted.

386
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:57,920
What? Did they find Baek Jin Ju?

387
00:26:59,520 --> 00:27:00,990
And what's this
about a press conference?

388
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:21,340
I see a chaotic morning coming.
What are those clowns up to?

389
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:29,250
Yes, Ms. Baek Jin Ju.

390
00:27:31,190 --> 00:27:32,790
I'm waiting at the police station.

391
00:27:33,790 --> 00:27:36,130
Don't worry, and get here safely.

392
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:37,960
Okay.

393
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,530
Baek Jin Ju...

394
00:27:45,100 --> 00:27:47,170
Is she on her way
to the committee meeting?

395
00:27:51,570 --> 00:27:52,580
Sir.

396
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:58,310
Sir, Baek Jin Ju is preparing
a press conference.

397
00:28:00,150 --> 00:28:03,320
- What?
- I heard Min Jun on the phone.

398
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:05,120
He said they rescued Baek Jin Ju,

399
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:08,020
and they're holding
a press conference to expose you.

400
00:28:08,430 --> 00:28:12,930
So, she faked her disappearance
and went into hiding,

401
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:15,670
just to stab me in the back
with a press conference?

402
00:28:17,100 --> 00:28:19,600
Find out where the press conference
is being held right now...

403
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:21,370
and capture Baek Jin Ju.

404
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:23,710
- Yes, sir.
- Sir.

405
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:28,340
- Baek Jin Ju is safe.
- I know.

406
00:28:28,980 --> 00:28:31,050
And because you failed
to take care of business,

407
00:28:31,050 --> 00:28:32,950
she's holding a press conference.

408
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:35,720
A press conference?
No, she's on her way to attend...

409
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:37,790
the reinvestigation review committee
hearing.

410
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:41,060
- What?
- What are you talking about?

411
00:28:41,060 --> 00:28:43,060
I heard she was holding
a press conference.

412
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:45,030
What do you mean?
I literally confirmed it...

413
00:28:45,030 --> 00:28:46,300
at the police station.

414
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:48,600
What the heck is going on?

415
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:50,670
Which one is it?

416
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:52,840
Sir.

417
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:57,240
Sir,
I've confirmed James's location.

418
00:28:57,710 --> 00:28:59,880
So, which one is it?

419
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:03,380
The press conference
or the review committee hearing?

420
00:29:03,950 --> 00:29:06,220
Actually,
he's at Secretary Jung's house.

421
00:29:08,250 --> 00:29:10,650
What? Check them all.

422
00:29:11,290 --> 00:29:13,360
The press conference,
the review committee hearing,

423
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:15,230
and Secretary Jung's house.

424
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:16,730
Send people to all of them,

425
00:29:17,730 --> 00:29:19,330
and find Baek Jin Ju!

426
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,000
What's this?

427
00:29:28,540 --> 00:29:31,410
That's right. Kim Dan Hui and James.

428
00:29:32,040 --> 00:29:34,210
The odds are high
she's here with both of you.

429
00:29:35,350 --> 00:29:37,280
Is this where Baek Jin Ju
has been hiding?

430
00:29:37,810 --> 00:29:38,920
Don't just stand there.

431
00:29:39,620 --> 00:29:41,580
- Find Baek Jin Ju right now.
- Yes, sir.

432
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:47,920
You shameless monster.

433
00:29:48,730 --> 00:29:50,960
How dare you come here
looking for Jin Ju?

434
00:29:51,230 --> 00:29:52,900
Park Tae Ho!

435
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,830
You failed to kill her
the first time,

436
00:29:55,900 --> 00:29:57,770
and now you've crawled back
to finish the job?

437
00:29:58,300 --> 00:30:01,170
If you lay one more finger
on Jin Ju,

438
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:03,640
you're going to have to deal
with me.

439
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,710
Why you...

440
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:08,710
- You have some nerve.
- What?

441
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,280
She's not here.

442
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:19,220
You must've hidden Baek Jin Ju
somewhere else,

443
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:22,260
but I'll catch her in the end.

444
00:30:23,930 --> 00:30:26,160
I've already sent my men
to the press conference...

445
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:27,430
and the review committee hearing.

446
00:30:28,930 --> 00:30:30,400
Catch her if you can.

447
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:33,100
That's assuming Jin Ju is even
at any of those places.

448
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:34,800
What?

449
00:30:35,470 --> 00:30:37,570
Don't tell me this was all a trick.

450
00:30:37,870 --> 00:30:38,880
That's right.

451
00:30:40,510 --> 00:30:43,850
This time, you're the one
who played right into our hands.

452
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:48,220
Now what happened seven years ago
will be revealed to the world,

453
00:30:48,890 --> 00:30:52,690
and the review committee
will decide to reinvestigate.

454
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,460
Unlike what happened 30 years ago,

455
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:56,290
the statute of limitations
hasn't expired for this,

456
00:30:57,030 --> 00:30:58,700
so you won't be able
to escape legal punishment.

457
00:31:04,230 --> 00:31:05,440
Where's Baek Jin Ju?

458
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:09,140
Where is she, and what's she up to?

459
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:17,750
(Incident Behind)

460
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:25,490
Today, we're diving into...

461
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:28,420
a mysterious incident
from seven years ago.

462
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:31,660
Joining us today is the victim
from that incident,

463
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:34,660
who is bravely coming forward...

464
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,600
to share her story.

465
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,970
Hello. I'm Baek Jin Ju.

466
00:31:45,780 --> 00:31:46,780
Today,

467
00:31:48,410 --> 00:31:50,610
I will release the documentary
I completed with Producer Shin...

468
00:31:51,980 --> 00:31:53,280
to the world.

469
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,150
Seven years ago,

470
00:31:57,520 --> 00:32:00,160
my father's life
was unjustly stolen.

471
00:32:02,130 --> 00:32:05,060
I'm publicly accusing the man
responsible for his murder.

472
00:32:05,860 --> 00:32:09,270
Chairman Park Tae Ho
of the Adele Group.

473
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:44,630
(Pearl in Red)

474
00:32:45,230 --> 00:32:47,840
- You did a great job.
- It's all thanks to your help.

475
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:52,380
Until Park Tae Ho is in prison,
let's all keep up the fight.

476
00:32:52,810 --> 00:32:54,510
Just stop Park Tae Ho
from being arrested.

477
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:56,610
If that buys Hyun Jun enough time
to become chairman,

478
00:32:56,750 --> 00:32:59,280
I'll make sure you're taken care of,
not Park Tae Ho.

479
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,720
That's not good enough.

480
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:03,520
I need a more concrete,
guaranteed reward.

481
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:04,950
Are you trying to stop
Father's arrest?

482
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:08,090
Are you going to keep getting
in Jin Ju's way on behalf of Father?

483
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:10,460
Weren't you the one
who saved her life?

484
00:33:10,530 --> 00:33:12,260
It seems Jin Ju
didn't tell you everything.

485
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:15,700
From now on, I'm not doing this for her,
but for myself.

486
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:18,500
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
